  "instructions_to_main_agent": [
    "Strictly follow the HS.fi / Bloomberg Businessweek editorial aesthetic.",
    "Do NOT use any gradients, heavy shadows, or aggressive rounding. Flat, clean, editorial UI is required.",
    "Use tabular-nums class for any score or statistic to ensure vertical alignment of digits.",
    "All interactive elements must have a data-testid attribute in kebab-case.",
    "The P*rkele-mittari dial should be the centerpiece component, accurately rendering the 5 states using the provided color tokens."
  ]
}